The Performance Review System
Your demonic manager Gary monitors two things: your soul count and your rejection rate. He sends passive aggressive messages when either looks bad. These appear as popup notifications in the corner of the screen. There is no timer — Gary just never stops watching.
"Hey just checking in on those soul numbers. No pressure but also kind of pressure. — Gary"
"Quick sync? Your acquisition rate is below the team average. The team average is demons who have been doing this for 400 years. — Gary"
"I need you to really bring your whole self to this. Your demonic whole self. — Gary"


3. Dual-View System
Overworld — Top-Down
A Pokemon-style top-down map of a small quirky town. The player walks freely, observes resident routines, and plans their approach. The intern carries a clipboard and a briefcase at all times.

Element
Description
Town layout
2-3 streets, a coffee shop, a town hall, a park, and residential homes
