Gary — Your Demon Manager
Gary is the passive aggressive Hell Inc. middle manager assigned to oversee your internship. He does not appear on the map but monitors your soul count and rejection rate obsessively. Notification popups appear whenever either metric looks bad. He is your comic antagonist — not threatening, just deeply, persistently annoying. He is your comic antagonist — not threatening, just deeply annoying.

Gary tracks two metrics: soul count and rejection rate. Messages trigger based on whichever looks worse at any given moment.

